  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) achieved below required level and is accepted via a documented offset rationale. Evidence carries explicitly-low confidence on material input scatter, fully documented with wide uncertainty bounds and a sensitivity analysis. Decision is Accepted with residual limitation acknowledged.",
