      "type": "OperatingEnvelope",
      "name": "F1717 compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Axial compressive load 0–2500 N applied at 5 mm/min crosshead speed; bending moment arm 60 mm per ASTM F1717 Section 8; construct angular displacement 0–40 mm; ambient temperature 23 +/- 2 deg C; screw diameter 7.5 mm non-cannulated Ti-6Al-4V; UHMWPE block geometry per F1717 Annex A1."
    },
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
