      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model with isotropic Ti-6Al-4V properties used up to yield; bilinear kinematic hardening applied post-yield. Model form selection justified by literature comparison and corroborated by three independent FEA implementations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) producing consistent predictions. Cross-model agreement within 3% for all QoIs supports model form adequacy.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
