      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Screws drawn from the same production lot as the model inputs. UHMWPE blocks sourced from a single certified batch. Sample traceability documented with serial numbers and lot certificates.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
