      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in FEA replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry: fixed inferior block, load applied at superior screw head via rigid coupling. Contact between screw shank and UHMWPE block modeled with frictional contact (mu = 0.15, measured). Crosshead displacement rate converted to quasi-static loading; inertial effects negligible at 5 mm/min. Parameter equivalency table documented in the validation plan.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
