      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared quantitatively: construct stiffness (2.0% error, E/uval 0.84), yield force (2.4% error, E/uval 1.12), and force at 40 mm displacement (1.4% error, E/uval 0.61). All E/uval values below 1.96 threshold. Uncertainty in experimental measurements (load cell calibration, displacement transducer) combined with model prediction uncertainty in denominator. Comparison documented in validation report VR-OUT-2024-01.",
